Package xyz.swatt.exceptions

This package will contain all of the custom SWATT Exceptions.

See: Description

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AbstractSwattException
    An Abstract Runtime Exception that all other Exceptions in the xyz.swatt.exceptions package inherit from.
    InvalidTypeException
    A generic Exception that should be thrown when one type is expected but another type is found.
    TooManyResultsException
    A generic Exception that should be thrown when more results are returned than expected.
    WebPageException
    This Exception is meant to be thrown by Selenium Web Page Classes.
    XmlException
    This Exception represents failures in XML parsing / manipulation.

Package xyz.swatt.exceptions Description

This package will contain all of the custom SWATT Exceptions.

These Exceptions will be kept generic, so that they will work in multiple situations.

Every Exception will extend the AbstractSwattException, so that they can all be caught under 1 ancestor class.

Every Exception will extend RuntimeException, so that it does not need to be declared as thrown.
